# Prisma migrations live here.
#
# To create the initial migration after wiring up your DB:
#   pnpm prisma migrate dev --name init
#
# That generates a timestamped subdirectory with an SQL file. Commit the
# generated files. CI/CD then runs `pnpm db:deploy` (which calls
# `prisma migrate deploy`) on every release.
#
# DO NOT edit migrations after they are committed. Create a new migration
# to alter or roll back instead.
